---
title: Fiesta Shrimp Bowls with Cilantro Rice and Lime Crema
description: Grab a plastic bib and get ready to tuck into a succulent shrimp dinner bursting with bold Tex-Mex flavours! Charred corn, juicy tomatoes, herbaceous cilantro rice and zippy lime crema come together to send your taste buds on a fiesta!
